  "description": "15 one-minute shorts created by various people from Japan's animation industry. The title of the collection, Ani*Kuri15, is abbreviated from the words \"anime\" and \"creators\".<br><br><strong>Season One</strong><br>\n1) Shinji Kimura - <em>Attack of Higashimachi Ni Chome/Attack of Higashimachi 2nd Burough</em><br>\n2) Akemi Hayashi - <em>Namida no Mukou/From the Other Side of the Tears</em><br>\n3) Yasufumi Soejima - <em>Hyotoko/Blaze Man</em><br>\n4) Osamu Kobayashi - <em>Sancha Blues/The Aromatic Tea Blues</em><br>\n5) Shinjiro Nishimi - <em>Uchujin Raikou Hiroshi no Baai/Invasion from Space - Hiroshi's Case</em><br><br>\n<strong>Season Two</strong><br>\n6) Mamoru Oshii - <em>Project Mermaid</em><br>\n7) Kazuto Nakazawa - <em>\"yurururu\" ~Nichijou Hen~</em><br>\n8) Range Murata and Tatsuya Yabuta - <em>Gyrosopter</em><br>\n9) Tobira Oda and Yasuyuki Shimizu - <em>Sport Captain Episode No.18: Assassin Descended from the Mountain Hunt!!</em><br>\n10) Atsushi Takeuchi - <em>Wandaba Kiss</em> <br><br>\n<strong>Season Three</strong><br>\n11) Makoto Shinkai - <em>Neko no Shuukai/A Gathering of Cats</em><br>\n12) Mahiro Maeda - <em>Onmitsu Hime</em><br>\n13) Michael Arias - <em>Okkakekko</em><br>\n14) Shouji Kawamori - <em>Project Omega</em><br>\n15) Satoshi Kon - <em>Ohayou/Good Morning</em>",
